{
  "stem": "12768.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then my father bought a villa-- what we called in Denmark a villa-- in a town called Hellerup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a little closer to Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it was, like, a private home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Before that, we lived in our own apartment house up on the fifth floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was too much for my mother to run up and down five flights of stairs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in those days, elevators wasn't modern.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that is one of the reasons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we moved to Hellerup in 1930.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was put into a kindergarten, which I walked to every day myself until I started school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I started school in 1933.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was Hellerup School, which just two years ago had a 100 years anniversary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So it is still standing and still used as a school today, is used as an international school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's-- I went to, to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I graduated at an early age because in Denmark, you don't have to-- if you don't have, what shall I say, the ambition to go the academic way, then-- I chose not to.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I chose then-- in Denmark, it's known that you would become an apprentice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was lucky to get an apprenticeship in a big mechanical company.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it was a little more taught the old-fashioned way of whatever you made, you made your own things, like blacksmithing and, and things like this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was, it was a hard journey, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On bicycle it took an hour, on bicycle to-- every day you had to be there at 7 o'clock in the morning, that meaning that I had to leave the house before 6:00.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I had to be up at 5:00, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
